<p>
Join the SIRS mailing list and be the first to know about our latest happenings. We will keep you informed of new and exciting courses and services available to suit your lifelong learning needs. You will also receive invitations to secure your seats for our upcoming events!
SIRS respect your privacy. The information you provide in this form will be used by SIRS to send you informational and promotional content related to SIRS only. We will keep your information confidential and not disclose it to any third party without prior written consent from you.
</p>
